{
  "id": "RAW_d0fd6f24",
  "title": "硅谷深陷算力荒：H200 一夜涨价 30%，H100 抢到缺货，Karpathy 也未能幸免",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651285214&idx=1&sn=2a56c4c18ce8de4a44d10a4b9b0ca2bb",
  "date": "2026-05-24 10:15:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: rgb(145, 145, 145);text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin: 13px 0px 0px;padding-left: 14px;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;\">作者 ｜ 四月 </span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;\">2026 年 5 月的硅谷，对于 AI 算力的“饥荒”和焦虑，正达到一个前所未有的高度。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;\">哪怕那些站在算力中心的人，也不得不开始为算力排队。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;\">在英伟达，负责应用深度学习研究团队的 Bryan Catanzaro 找黄仁勋申请训练卡。最近大家一直抱怨卡不够用，受限太多。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;\">“不好意思，那些卡已经卖掉了”，这是老黄给出的回复。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;\">Catanzaro 是英伟达的大功臣。十多年前，正是他留意到，GPU 迎来了首批 AI 买家——研究员，且几乎疯狂扫货。基于这个洞察，老黄才下定决心把整间公司押注 AI 赛道。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__6\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>当年帮英伟达赌对算力卡的人，现在却买不到自家的 GPU 了。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__7\"><span>而比“卖铲子的没铲子了”更戏剧性的事，还发生在谷歌。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__8\"><span>去年夏天，DeepMind 的研究员 Andrew Dai 判断，视觉推理是个值得做的方向。于是向公司内部提了一批 TPU 的资源需求。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__9\"><span>但申请迟迟未批。拒绝的理由，倒不是研究方向不够好，而是项目不能为下一代的 Gemini 服务。当时的内部原则是，资源应该优先流向付费客户和旗舰模型。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__10\"><span>“在谷歌内部，每一块 TPU 的背后，都有三位竞争者”，华盛顿大学计算机系的荣誉教授 Oren Etzioni 聊到。现实很残酷，如果你的项目不能直接带来收入，你就是在和付费客户抢资源。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__11\"><span>Dai 最终选择离职创业。和他做出同样选择的，还有 Anna Goldie。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__12\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>有趣的是，谷歌用来挽留 Goldie 的筹码不是加薪，也不是期权，而是——更多的 TPU 算力卡。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__13\"><span>但 Goldie 还是走了，还拿到了 3.35 亿美元的融资，“这笔钱能买到的算力，和当初 DeepMind 挽留我开出的条件，几乎相当。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__14\"><span>当大厂围墙内的算力变成一种“组织权限”，出走就成了唯一解。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__15\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>而在围墙之外，独立开发者和研究员面对的，是比“GPU 短缺”更难的处境：连卡都租不到。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__16\"><span>这事已经迫切到什么程度了呢？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__17\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8063b5a7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm4hymhMgDXF59AqETXj81DysgGoSWl6nfySaVLoQqAtW0ZkNCIQ6w5AOf5vKm76XyP3BiayriaMyGXkUn0VYbqloVl39M49E0FE8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__18\"><span>这两天，AI 大神 Andrej Karpathy 都忍不住发帖吐槽。他表示，在录制 nanochat 教学视频时，才突然意识到，如果实验的第一步是，让学员“从云平台启动一台 8×H100 的服务器”，那么绝大部分人将倒在起跑线上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__19\"><span>有大神出来喊话，评论区迅速变成大型比惨现场。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bbd78f6e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNjV2B57wEsMwPToBjYzX4CTwAAzQsF8o9XW4S33sicJlgrhYJNicdUCia7cV2xF7QibsPPBPB8m7X41FNMf7VcEKbZxfp07ebXZ3wE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span>1</span></span><span>&nbsp;H100 抢不到，H200 一夜涨价 30% </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__22\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bab9b0da&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm7ze6QgibQL67hW90f8aAvicEEkTln5l9HQkIJ1L1FFhzanRj6PUhxJzSLLlauVpaeybUHibskmsCXbFhfREhobbcEJ6et9yN1SeQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D2\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__23\"><span>看这话问得，显然是我方友军无疑了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__24\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e851a44e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5W88b0NNwSibEMZl1qupkSzialLPsmDNYlxPibVWUGicjeibpTOQVNcxHqqp5mtGtHdnNv9qnEOhXictwr3Nm3Hb7z1ArbJLmrYndiaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__25\"><span>有人补刀，其实真正的第一步，还不是启动 Server，而是求爷爷告奶奶等 quota approval。 现在大多数的普通用户，是连 8×H100 的预审批权限都没有的。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__26\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=12556036&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5Atvpicwga8whNr1soF0EiblBEicR0Ium3nbw1QKrWCrLJ5hpicPiauX5nX6wdCHibHfCvbsMTB2VbFspqNt6VXXu2GLQnao7xZgbXs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D4\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__27\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=794dadd9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm7EDqlYCzTBeXUkqPRL1yeag17X2VZwgaVm8OLEAy3A1XFiaAujfRtI1CiaHpr5DkK7l8MSN83Iy2DgFmqLlHRvKuHXfBuqZKQsY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__28\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54f7b597&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6Fkk39jBYhhqBDF4VI4tabGct219v9c3w5HL2iajiaX0UnBolKZmygWsBmuSPB3Y8CcSExwgC935ADzguhsvhuA9V2iaZicNBDBuw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D6\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__29\"><span>更有开发者直接晒后台截图：RunPod 上多种 GPU 型号显示 unavailable；Azure 上 H100 虚拟机启动失败，提示 capacity 不足；Google Colab 选择 GPU 后，被系统自动降档到 G4。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__30\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f518c956&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5gu8v6camTNQNULHy4yof5b3xMYfnIqkA936GicdWaxuhwdSu9zzpclIlnxZTTgTOWTQEHYEE5oaQG8ZwRHkyWdTiaB3ljBzNjY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D7\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__31\"><span>Rohan Bansal 看着账户里仅存的两个 H100 实例，发了条推文：“holding on for dear life”。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__32\"><span>如果说资源紧缺必然导致价格上涨，尚可理解。但这涨价的姿势未免也有些诡异。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__33\"><span>正常的逻辑是，新一代出来，旧款降价。B200 已经稳定供货，四年前的 H100 也理应降价。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__34\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df9e544f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm5be8ibs5twZEZiavJWAhcDXUIib4jHznjP2ysMjuxygZwM61eyrSdpzFX4IPSo9VNFBw2EFYnvyVNrfdz3hrViaic8Xu5Geuddgaiao%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D8\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__35\"><span>但 SemiAnalysis 数据显示，H100 一年期的合约租金，半年涨了近 40%（从 2025 年 10 月的 $1.70/ 小时，涨到 2026 年 3 月的 $2.35）。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__36\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=131b9669&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm6T2TZALhrjiaLbLBZApEnlVwOrFeG5b4H5OSsSp18qbtDKiafJSU8NG15KuqRQygKMktycvn2HOnzCcycS06er8hiaX2jEkLXN7U%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D9\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__37\"><span>现货市场更夸张，lambda 的报价已上浮到 4 美元 +/ 小时，是两年前的两倍。而 H200 的现货价格甚至比新一代 B200 还要贵。\"这价格是两年前的两倍还多，而且通常很难抢到，要写脚本盯着 API 才有机会。\"</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__38\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"width: 649px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=33f656a4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FlYDricib2fsm7BsLAeaoNd2ll5XCCD1agAyVGyR2WA7TKHjtJuqDu3O0MZHVmLLILtLg2Je2X1VljZjxmic0xKeNFLuy6KPMdc5ia9TiaV4gsAJ0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D10\"></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" class=\"js_darkmode__39\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图注：从 4.96 美元 / 小时涨到 6.40 美元 / 小时，涨幅 29%；而更新一代的 B200 为 5.68 美元 /GPU 小时。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=317ef9d0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNiaLhQLxFgwLJA8ibwtF6SwickpicpzqDlXceEApEehhnxoDCu7VVu6smU2YToZZXzw38WOdDBkAEw3eSQeHtdGTqppCWOmmcoKibvU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span>2</span></span><span>&nbsp;5% 的利用率和 B200 的倒挂 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__42\"><span>一边是高端 GPU 紧缺，一边却是算力中心里的利用率低得令人发指。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__43\"><span>Cast AI 的报告显示，不少大企业 GPU 集群的平均利用率只有 5% 左右。此前，马斯克的兆瓦级算力中心 Colossus 的 MFU（模型算力利用率）仅为 11% 左右。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__44\"><span>其实并不是企业意识到不到算力资源的浪费，而是不敢放手。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__45\"><span>排队几个月，云厂商销售突然打电话：“你要的卡现在只剩 36 张了，只能签一年的长约。不要的话，后面还有五家排队等着呢。”</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__46\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>这时候，问题已经不是“公司是否需要租用这么长时间的芯片”，而是“我敢不敢错过这笔订单”。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__47\"><span>先签下来，哪怕闲置也不释放，因为交出去的算力卡可能就再也拿不回来了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__48\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>芯片不只是产能短缺，更是流动性短缺：</span></strong><span>&nbsp;它卡在企业的算力长约里，困在云厂商的容量池里，但就是不在普通开发者今晚能点开购买的页面上。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__49\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>短缺制造恐慌，恐慌制造囤积，囤积制造更深的短缺。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__50\"><span>而这种流动性的枯竭，也放大了另一个结构性问题：为什么偏偏是 H100/H200 被推上了天价，甚至比新一代 B200 还贵？</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__51\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>因为算力市场从来不是按“谁更新”来定价，而是按“谁更好用、更好接入”来定价的。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__52\"><span>过去大家抢 GPU，想象中的场景是巨头训练下一代大模型，当然要追求极致先进。但现在，消耗 GPU 的地方变多了：推理服务、代码 Agent、RL 后训练、自动评测、小模型复现、教学实验，都在持续吃算力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__53\"><span>对于这些海量需求来说，B200 代表的下一代性能上限并不是首选。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__54\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>做工程的人最懂：最先进不等于最好用，真正值钱的是确定性。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__55\"><span>H100/H200 足够强，且生态足够成熟。你用 H100 跑，别人的 benchmark 也是 H100；你用 H200 做推理，调参经验已经有人踩过坑。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__56\"><span>相比之下，新一代芯片再强，也需要时间消化到框架、集群、调度和成本模型里。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__57\"><span>训练市场还没完全切到 Blackwell，推理和后训练市场又把需求重重叠加上来。旧卡本该退场，却因为“确定性”成了刚需。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d18fb0b9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNgprgrAum8YOFFknibrmmkZico8hdO1kAXEwxz4jbHiaJZvo08qKRZgv5Eic8B0DRpK4DgPHjBjaF2u7dzVwtreUHsTHkuEbgktIVM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span>3</span></span><span>&nbsp;AI 民主化，卡在了算力门槛上</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__60\"><span>这一轮的芯片荒，和过去还不太一样。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__61\"><span>过去聊缺芯，是顶级 AI Lab 的军备竞赛，巨头谁抢到更多 GPU，谁就能训练更大模型。但这一次，焦虑正在往下沉。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__62\"><span>Karpathy 录教程要先考虑开发者能不能拿到 8×H100；LocalLLaMA 社区讨论能不能用本地 Mac 硬跑；高校研究员担心拿不到算力，小团队担心扩容被大客户挤掉。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__63\"><span>这背后已经不是“我要训练 GPT-5”的野心，而是一个更朴素的问题：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>我只是想复现一个实验，为什么第一步就变成抢算力了？</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__64\"><span>AI 开源这几年确实降低了许多门槛。模型权重可以下载，代码可以 fork。但算力把另一扇门关上了。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__65\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>代码可以开源，但 H100 不能 fork。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__66\"><span>真正的 AI 研究从来不只是看懂代码，还得你能跑通实验、复现结果，调参、失败，以及很多次的再重来。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__67\"><span>如果每次实验的前提，都是拿到一组昂贵且不稳定的 GPU，那么开源的平等，就会被算力的不平等重新抵消。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__68\"><span>从 Google 研究员离职创业，到英伟达内部争 GPU，然后是 Karpathy 的教学视频卡在 8 张 H100，它们指向同一件事：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>算力正在从基础设施，变成一种筛选机制。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__69\"><span>它筛掉的未必是没有想法的人，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span>而是没有预算、没有配额资源、没有长期合同的群体。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__70\"><span>这才是 AI 民主化最尴尬的现实：模型越来越开放，但能跑起来的人，可能并没有变多。</span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight: 400;font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 20px;color: #00b38b;text-align: left;line-height: 35px;margin: 40px 8px 0 8px;background: none no-repeat left 28px;background-size: 100% 6px;background-image: url(&quot;https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c4d476c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FhLLZnAbUwNiajuPluwzTDoyllwDJPUelJPjEmvgZtpKqicjsWVwqboqpAusJx1Eercvx92UpCPftWO0WUzibtZ8Dwt7QkRHiaaoIlc75eMoicG7E%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg&quot;);\"><span style=\"display: block;font-size: 32px;margin-bottom: 10px;padding-left: 22px;\"><span>4</span></span><span>&nbsp;国内开发者的痛：过渡期的双重压力 </span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__73\"><span>把视线拉回国内，如果说海外开发者是在成熟生态里抢 H100/H200 现货；那么国内开发者面对的，则是过渡期的多重压力考验，要在新的算力结构里找\"能用且好用\"的解法。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__74\"><span>某云 H100 排期已到 2027 年第一季度，更多的云平台同样面临高端卡供应瓶颈，\"有钱也租不到\"是真实的用户反馈。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__75\"><span>与此同时，高端卡的获取仍然受政策影响，当然国产算力替代正在加速。但从 CUDA 体系切换的工程成本是真实存在的，适配层、代码改动、调试周期，对小团队而言不是轻松的迁移。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__76\"><span>其实，大家底层的处境不尽相同。算力底座从来不是一个宏大词，而是非常具体的体验——实例能不能启动，价格扛不扛得住，实验结果能不能复现。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0 8px;margin:0;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\" class=\"js_darkmode__77\"><span>今天 AI 圈真正稀缺的，也许不是最新的芯片，而是普通人能稳定拿到、马上用起来、跑出结果的有效算力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__78\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"color:#888888;font-size:14px;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__79\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">Even Nvidia’s own research teams can’t get enough GPUs amid the race for AI computing power（<a href=\"https://fortune.com/2026/04/09/nvidia-gpu-shortage-impacts-even-nvidias-own-research-teams-bryan-catanzaro-eye-on-ai/）\" target=\"_blank\">https://fortune.com/2026/04/09/nvidia-gpu-shortage-impacts-even-nvidias-own-research-teams-bryan-catanzaro-eye-on-ai/）</a></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#888888;font-size:14px;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__81\"><strong style=\"background-color:transparent;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.034em;\" class=\"js_darkmode__82\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">The Great GPU Shortage – Rental Capacity – Launching our H100 1 Year Rental Price Index（<a href=\"https://newsletter.semianalysis.com/p/the-great-gpu-shortage-rental-capacity\" target=\"_blank\">https://newsletter.semianalysis.com/p/the-great-gpu-shortage-rental-capacity</a></span></span><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">）</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#888888;font-size:14px;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__83\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">FOMO is why enterprises pay for GPUs they don't use — and why prices keep climbing（</span></span><strong style=\"background-color:transparent;white-space:break-spaces;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.034em;\" class=\"js_darkmode__84\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://venturebeat.com/infrastructure/fomo-is-why-enterprises-pay-for-gpus-they-dont-use-and-why-prices-keep-climbing\" target=\"_blank\">https://venturebeat.com/infrastructure/fomo-is-why-enterprises-pay-for-gpus-they-dont-use-and-why-prices-keep-climbing</a></span></span></strong><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">）</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#888888;font-size:14px;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__85\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://semianalysis.com/gpu-pricing-index/\" target=\"_blank\">https://semianalysis.com/gpu-pricing-index/</a></span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#888888;font-size:14px;\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;\" class=\"js_darkmode__86\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">Nvidia A100 vs H100 vs B200 GPU Rental Price and Performance（</span></span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\"><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\"><a href=\"https://ornn.com/insights/nvidia-a100-vs-h100-vs-b200-gpu-rental-price-and-performance\" target=\"_blank\">https://ornn.com/insights/nvidia-a100-vs-h100-vs-b200-gpu-rental-price-and-performance</a></span></span></strong><span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: normal;\">）</span></span></strong></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <div class=\"js_darkmode__194\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <div class=\"js_darkmode__199\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"></div>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "2026 年 5 月的硅谷正经历前所未有的 AI 算力荒，H100/H200 价格飙升、一卡难求，连英伟达内部团队和谷歌研究员都难以获取足够算力，算力正从基础设施变成一种筛选机制。",
